                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nLoperamide is an antidiarrheal agent commonly administered after the client experiences loose stools. It is used to treat both acute diarrhea and chronic diarrhea from disorders such as inflammatory bowel disease. It also can be used to reduce the volume of drainage from an ileostomy.",
